content: Baw-Lang-Lang is one of the six frog bosses you can find in Black Myth: Wukong. The fifth of the frogs, Baw-Lang-Lang can only be discovered once you've taken down the Five Element Carts and gained access to Bishui Cave.

The content is as follows:
Baw-Lang-Lang is one of the six frog bosses you can find in Black Myth: Wukong. The fifth of the frogs, Baw-Lang-Lang can only be discovered once you've taken down the Five Element Carts and gained access to Bishui Cave.
